Art App	

‘Art App’ would Daily Art Challenge that would utilize a random generator

Would accept input from users and suggest them something to draw

Would store users’ (Profile/Log-In feature) artworks on a database

Allow users to ‘like’ other users’ artworks.

Users get ‘points’ for completing art challenges (Drawing suggestions, art quizzes, art contests) – giving users something to work towards.

Allow users to ‘tag’ their artworks with keywords

Suggest artwork based on what the users ‘like’ (Using cookies or caching)	
